@c -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
@anchor{binomial}
@deffn {Fun@,{c}@~{a}o} binomial (@var{x}, @var{y})

O coeficiente binaomial @code{@var{x}!/(@var{y}! (@var{x} - @var{y})!)}.
